  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\"><img alt=\"Brotherhood without banners.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/50px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/75px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/100px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Dennet</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\"><img alt=\"Brotherhood without banners.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/50px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/75px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/100px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Dennett_TheMico.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Dennett TheMico.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f5/Dennett_TheMico.jpg/250px-Dennett_TheMico.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"354\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f5/Dennett_TheMico.jpg/375px-Dennett_TheMico.jpg 1.5x, /images/f/f5/Dennett_TheMico.jpg 2x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nDennett<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ser\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ser\">Ser</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\">Brotherhood without banners</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Dennet</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> (or <b>Dennett</b>)<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\">brotherhood without banners</a>. He is a longbowman.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dennet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dennet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Dennet is present when <a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a> is given a <a href=\"/index.php/Trial_by_combat\" title=\"Trial by combat\">trial by combat</a> by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Beric_Dondarrion\" title=\"Beric Dondarrion\">Beric Dondarrion</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Hollow_hill\" title=\"Hollow hill\">hollow hill</a>. Dennet, <a href=\"/index.php/Anguy\" title=\"Anguy\">Anguy</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Kyle_(brotherhood)\" title=\"Kyle (brotherhood)\">Kyle</a> are ordered to feather the <a href=\"/index.php/Hound\" title=\"Hound\">Hound</a> at the first sign of treachery, and only after all three bowmen have their shafts notched does <a href=\"/index.php/Thoros_of_Myr\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Thoros of Myr\">Thoros of Myr</a> hand Sandor a belt.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dennet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\"